Included page: .ScenarioLibrary (edit)

These scenarios will be accessible to all test cases in the the FitNesseRoot folder. If you are using a different FitNesseRoot Folder, make sure to copy these files if using any setup scenarios.


Update these variables for your specific test environment


  • Expand
  • Collapse

Variables for Scenarios

Default browser can be FIREFOX, CHROME, or IE
variable defined: defaultBrowser=CHROME

Default Version can be 17.2, 17.1, 16.3, 16.2, 16.1, 7.11, or 7.10
variable defined: defaultVersion=18.1

Default Locale can be en_US or en_GB
variable defined: defaultLocale=en_US

Default URL should include http or https and /suite (e.g. https://forum.appian.com/suite )
variable defined: defaultUrl=REPLACE_APPIAN_URL

To use out of the box functionality, do not update the scenarios below

  • Collapse

Setup customizable for browser, locale, version, and URL

scenario setup for test script for browser browserType locale location version versionNum url appianUrl
setup with browser @browserType
set appian locale to @location
set appian version to @versionNum
set appian url to @appianUrl
set timeout seconds to 20
set start datetime

script
setup with browser FIREFOX
login with username U14258394

Create Travel Request with expenses WHERE USER HAS A DEFAULT CHARTFIELD


script
click on menu Actions
click on link Create Expense Report
click on radio option Expense Report for Mileage/Incidentals Only
click on button Next
click on radio option My Travelers
populate field Search by Employee ID with 00000045734
click on link Search
select grid [1] row [1]
verify grid [2] row [1] is selected
click on button Next
populate field Description with FitNess for Archivum Test
populate field Business Purpose with Administrative Meeting
populate field Comment with FitNess for Archivum Test
click on radio option Tampa Campus
populate field Point of Origin with Tampa
populate field Start Time with 8:00 AM
populate field End Time with 5:00 PM
populate grid [1] column Start Date row [1] with +0 days
populate grid [1] column End Date row [1] with +0 days
populate grid [1] column Destination row [1] with sarasota
click on button Enter Accounting Defaults
click on button Enter Expense Details
click on link Add New Expense(s)
populate field Expense Type with Incidentals In State
populate field Date with 09/29/2017
populate field Amount with 30.00
click on radio option Paid by Cash/Check
populate field Description with FitNesse Test
click on button Save Expense
click on button Manage Receipts
populate FILE_UPLOAD field [1] with c:/FitNesseForAppian/FitNesseRoot/files/blankDocs/test.pdf
click on radio option Print and Sign
click on button Submit
populate field Upload Approval Document with c:/FitNesseForAppian/FitNesseRoot/files/blankDocs/test.pdf
click on button Submit
logout
tear down
